{"body": "@tenderlove Wouldn't calling ```save``` execute callbacks and validations?\nperhaps something like this:\n\n```ruby\ndef update_columns(attributes)\n  raise ActiveRecordError, \"can not update on a new record object\" unless persisted?\n  attributes.each_key {|key| raise ActiveRecordError, \"#{key.to_s} is marked as readonly\" if self.class.readonly_attributes.include?(key.to_s) }\n  assign_attributes(attributes)\n  self.class.update_all(attributes, self.class.primary_key => id) == 1\nend\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5771254", "created_at": "2012-05-17T18:52:53Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1190#issuecomment-5771254", "updated_at": "2012-05-17T18:52:53Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 1190, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/smartinez87", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/47e6725dce64c265920bb1fc8fa3f74c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F4cfa4655130c014a5a9ffdaaefcdaae1.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/received_events", "gravatar_id": "47e6725dce64c265920bb1fc8fa3f74c", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "smartinez87", "type": "User", "id": 83449, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/smartinez87/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52385be6bd3543c151011e9e"}, "id": 5771254, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1190"}
